      "content": "sounds good. go ahead and write the first few paragraphs. i want it to really lean into the contrast between the \"traditional values\" we're protecting and the \"radicalism\" we're fighting against. use strong language—don't hold back on calling out the progressive agenda for what it is. i want the crowd to feel like this is a fight for the soul of the country.",
